      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for the declared model risk level.",
      "rationale": "Iterative solver residuals were monitored and converged below 1e-6 for all load steps. Nonlinear convergence was confirmed via force and displacement norm criteria."
    },
