      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for the declared model risk level.",
      "rationale": "Linear elastic material models are appropriate for the titanium alloy screw and UHMWPE block in the sub-yield compression-bending regime. Contact formulation (augmented Lagrangian, frictional) is well-established for this class of orthopaedic implant simulation."
    },
    {
