    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for a Model Risk Level 3 assessment. The single below-required factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted under the Medium assurance level threshold because the single-angle ASTM F1717 protocol is the regulatory standard and additional load-angle variation is outside the defined submission scope. Overall credibility is sufficient to support the intended regulatory decision.",
